# Persistence Backend Artifacts
# SQLiteBackend emits three files in WAL mode: the main .db, plus -shm / -wal
# sidecars. The scaffold in CONTRIBUTING.md uses cascadeui.db by name, so any
# contributor running the dev bot drops these in the working tree.
*.db
*.db-shm
*.db-wal
*.db-journal
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3